uet","Date":"1647","Medium":"etching with engraving on laid paper","CreditLine":"Katharine Shepard Fund","URL":"https://www.nga.gov/artworks/204071","ImageURL":"https://api.nga.gov/iiif/5772f5e0-5c78-4052-b3fe-d3eaa361c9ec/full/!800,800/0/default.jpg"},{"ObjectID":206766,"Title":"Riverbank at Night","Artist":"Charles Émile Jacque","Date":"1844","Medium":"etching on wove paper","CreditLine":"Purchased as the Gift of Andrew Robison","URL":"https://www.nga.gov/artworks/206766","ImageURL":"https://api.nga.gov/iiif/83ceaaea-4e2f-43c4-9f15-7d28364870ab/full/!800,800/0/default.jpg"},{"ObjectID":213234,"Title":"Saint  Anthony with the Christ Child","Artist":"Italian 17th Century(?)","Date":"1641","Medium":"etching on laid paper","CreditLine":"Gift of Alessandra Manning Dolnier","URL":"https://www.nga.gov/artworks/213234","ImageURL":"https://api.nga.gov/iiif/3531c070-0d9d-44fa-9e97-9f40929b6518/full/!800,800/0/default.jpg"},{"ObjectID":215390,"Title":"View of Ticonderoga from Lake Champlain","Artist":"Charles B. J. Févret de Saint-Mémin","Date":"1794-1796","Medium":"etching with hand coloring on laid paper mounted to brown wove paper","CreditLine":"Corcoran Collection (Gift of William Wilson Corcoran)","URL":"https://www.nga.gov/artworks/215390","ImageURL":"https://api.nga.gov/iiif/3d1bb529-ddc9-421e-9c09-aecf85806340/full/!800,800/0/default.jpg"},{"ObjectID":215929,"Title":"Inscription [reverse]","Artist":"George Hampden Lovett","Date":"1889","Medium":"white metal","CreditLine":"Corcoran Collection (Gift of E.P. Whaites)","URL":"https://www.nga.gov/artworks/215929","ImageURL":"https://api.nga.gov/iiif/24a7656c-b147-4133-af58-8915d3f70fe4/full/!800,800/0/default.jpg"},{"ObjectID":217007,"Title":"Carte photographique de la lune, planche I (Photographic Chart of the Moon, plate I)","Artist":"Charles le Morvan","Date":"February 23, 1909, printed 1914","Medium":"photogravure with ink on tissue paper overlay","CreditLine":"Pepita Milmore Memorial Fund","URL":"https://www.nga.gov/